snippet.title: Venineth 🌑 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
🛒 Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/976500/Venineth/ 
🌑 Venineth is a single-player game focusing on unraveling the mysteries of ancient alien technology somewhere in the universe via exploration, platforming, and puzzle-solving, in dangerous, distant worlds. 

Visit the project website for more info: www.venineth.blogspot.com
Publisher's website: www.monadrock.com
Follow the project on Twitter: www.twitter.com/VeninethGame
Music by EchoRay: www.facebook.com/EchoRay-279843596261627

#Venineth #Game #GameDev
